Description: MultiFlexi web interface core components
 Core PHP classes and web interface components for MultiFlexi.
 Contains the main application logic and web interface files including
 dashboard, company management, job management, administrative tools,
 and GDPR-compliant consent management system with cookie policy support.
 Includes GDPR Article 16 compliance features for data rectification,
 user profile management, approval workflows, and comprehensive audit logging.
 GDPR Phase 3 Security Enhancements: comprehensive security audit logging,
 AES-256 data encryption for sensitive information, API rate limiting with
 configurable endpoint protection, and IP whitelisting for administrative access control.

